Emma: Huh...I guess we are not welcomed after all...I don't feel like entering the fairy forest like this… I wish I could at least meet the chief of the Fairy Forest, Lady Frecia, in person, but she doesn't come all the way out here.  #line:ch3_FairyForest_26

